msgstr "Anchor diversity: 100% = every link has a different anchor. Below 60% = over-optimization risk."

msgid "Zsynchronizowano %d stron, %d w striking distance."
msgstr "Synced %d pages, %d in striking distance."

msgid "dodaj email Service Account jako użytkownika (Pełne uprawnienia lub Ograniczone)"
msgstr "add Service Account email as user (Full or Restricted access)"

